Package com.glitchybyte.lib.log

Class GLog

java.lang.Object
com.glitchybyte.lib.log.GLog
public final class GLog
extends java.lang.Object
Logger class.

Implements a nice time format and shows thread name. Made to log one liners (except for exceptions). Set logger name before use to change default name. Default logging level is CONFIG.
